My friend's rehearsal dinner was at a karaoke bar in Las Vegas. I got to Vegas late, so I took a cab straight from the airport to the bar. The bride saw me come in, slammed $20 and a filled out slip on the DJ booth, pointed at me and said "She sings next."

It was What a Fool Believes. Crushed it.
